{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"14a4ca643b","title":"朱光潜应继续深入检查 分清敌我界限站稳立场","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f65d6a3c98","index":0,"year":1951,"month":12,"day":3,"articleId":"14a4ca643b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"b071d938b1","name":"赵瑞芝"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3290b5bd5c","type":"title","text":"朱光潜应继续深入检查 分清敌我界限站稳立场","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"14a4ca643b"},{"id":"2126b36454","type":"authors","text":"赵瑞芝","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"14a4ca643b"},{"id":"49ba4f5703","type":"paragraph","text":"编辑同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"14a4ca643b"},{"id":"1b0332901d","type":"paragraph","text":"从朱光潜“最近学习中几点检讨”一文看来，他在这次教师学习运动中有了一些进步。但是我觉得朱光潜的检讨是不够深刻的，他还没有把过去的错误思想完全暴露出来，并作批判。他虽用了不少“超阶级”、“超政治”等字眼，但对于他过去的反动的言论和行动，却说得很少。他只是抽象地说“我站上了反动派的立场，替反动派服务”。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"14a4ca643b"},{"id":"1f48e84ad7","type":"paragraph","text":"朱光潜曾提到他过去“任过伪中央委员”，“赴过蒋介石的宴会”，“加入了国民党”，“调到‘中央训练团’受过训”。从这里看来，朱光潜确曾推动过那座反动机器，而且他所起的反动作用并不很小。希望朱光潜对自己的过去进行进一步的检查，否则，他今后怎么能分清敌我，站稳立场呢？","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"14a4ca643b"},{"id":"6f4f2fa156","type":"paragraph","text":"赵瑞芝","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"14a4ca643b"},{"id":"43c10a08a9","type":"paragraph","text":"1951年12月3日人民日报电子版","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"14a4ca643b"},{"id":"d7b9126107","type":"paragraph","text":"","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"14a4ca643b"}],"page":{"id":"be22d6bcf9","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"14a4ca643b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}